## Card that shows what cards go with a pilot/upgrade/mech
{% macro build_meta_card(type) %}
    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
            <span class="card-name">{{ type.human_name() }}</span>
            <span class="card-number">{{ type.card_types |count }}</span>
        </div>
        <img src="images/{{ type.name }}.png" class="card-image">
        <div class="card-body">
            {% for card_type in type.card_types %}
                <p>{{ 'â€£' + card_type.human_name() }}</p>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
        <div class="card-footer">{{ type.flavor_text }}</div>
    </div>
{% endmacro %}
